<h1>Study Reminder App</h1>

<p>
This app helps users manage study reminders using Google Calendar.
Users can create events based on learning content and receive notifications.
</p>

<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>This application uses Google Calendar API to create and manage study reminder events.</p>

<p><strong>Information We Access</strong><br>
Google Calendar data (read and write access)</p>

<p><strong>Purpose of Use</strong><br>
To create and manage calendar events for study reminders</p>

<p><strong>Data Storage</strong><br>
No user data is stored on external servers<br>
All additional data is stored locally on the user's device</p>

<p><strong>Data Sharing</strong><br>
This app does not share user data with any third parties</p>

<p><strong>User Control</strong><br>
Users can revoke access at any time via their Google account settings</p>

